                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        Or you can install it via <a href="http://docs.nuget.org/docs/start-here/using-the-package-manager-console" target="_blank">Package Manager Console</a>
                    </p>
                    <div class="col-md-11">
                        <code class="nuget-badge">
                            PM> Install-Package Nelibur
